The paper focuses on recommender systems and their connection to revenue maximization, which is a topic that falls under information retrieval (cs.IR) and game theory (cs.GT). The paper also proposes a novel model and algorithm for solving the revenue-maximizing recommendation problem, which involves optimization and algorithm design, falling under data structures (cs.DS), machine learning (cs.LG), and economics and computation (cs.EC).
